<section class="wb-lab" data-agent-chat-lab>
  <header class="wb-lab__header">
    <span class="wb-lab__eyebrow">互动 01</span>
    <h2 class="wb-lab__title">同一句话，两种完全不同的结果</h2>
    <p class="wb-lab__description">切换查看：一个给你建议，一个把任务推进到可验收的产物。</p>
  </header>

  <div class="wb-field">
    <span>你的要求</span>
    <div class="wb-card wb-mono">把这份会议记录整理成正式会议纪要。</div>
  </div>

  <div class="wb-choice-row" role="tablist" aria-label="结果类型">
    <button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" data-mode="chat">普通聊天</button>
    <button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-mode="agent">WorkBuddy 任务</button>
  </div>

  <div class="comparison-output" role="tabpanel" data-panel="chat">
    <div class="wb-card">
      <h3>它告诉你怎么做</h3>
      <p>“你可以先提取会议主题，再整理关键结论和待办事项。”</p>
      <p class="wb-status warning">停在建议：文件还要你自己打开、整理和保存。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="comparison-output" role="tabpanel" data-panel="agent" hidden>
    <ol class="agent-steps">
      <li><span>1</span><div><strong>理解目标</strong><p>确认输入文件、输出格式和验收标准。</p></div></li>
      <li><span>2</span><div><strong>拟定计划</strong><p>读取记录、提取事实、生成纪要、保存文件。</p></div></li>
      <li><span>3</span><div><strong>请求确认</strong><p>让你先看计划和文件范围。</p></div></li>
      <li><span>4</span><div><strong>生成产物</strong><p>交付 <code>meeting-summary.md</code>。</p></div></li>
      <li><span>5</span><div><strong>人工验收</strong><p>你检查内容、格式和保存位置。</p></div></li>
    </ol>
    <p class="wb-status success">走到交付：但最后的“合格”仍由你判断。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[data-agent-chat-lab]').forEach((root) => {
    const tabs = [...root.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('[role="tab"]')];
    const panels = [...root.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[role="tabpanel"]')];

    tabs.forEach((tab) => {
      tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const mode = tab.dataset.mode;
        tabs.forEach((item) => item.setAttribute('aria-selected', String(item === tab)));
        panels.forEach((panel) => {
          panel.hidden = panel.dataset.panel !== mode;
        });
      });
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .comparison-output {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .agent-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .agent-steps li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: var(--control-height) 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .agent-steps li > span {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    inline-size: var(--control-height);
    block-size: var(--control-height);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    background: var(--color-bg-info);
    color: var(--color-text-info);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .agent-steps p {
    margin: var(--space-1) 0 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }
</style>
